Crobat (TCG)

From Bulbapedia, the community-driven Pokémon encyclopedia.
Jump to navigationJump to search
← #0168: Ariados
Pokémon
#0170: Chinchou →
For Pokémon TCG Pocket cards, see Crobat (TCG Pocket).

Crobat has been featured on 27 different cards since it debuted in the Neo Revelation expansion of the Pokémon Trading Card Game. Crobat cards are normally Darkness-type Stage 2 Pokémon.

List of Pokémon cards featuring Crobat

Crobat
Cards listed with a blue background are only legal to use in the current Expanded format.
Cards listed with a green background are legal to use in both the current Standard and Expanded formats.
